{"tid":1936751,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪所有男仔都係咁","createTime":"2020-03-21T12:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T08:38:16.000Z","uid":353460,"like":2,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3603392e70b279ce425158447d3c4923a03adb50","tid":1936751,"uid":353460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"今年陪條仔考多次DSE<br />\n每幾日同佢傾幾分鐘電話<br />\n佢就話佢要溫習<br />\n雖然睇到佢ig sc post話佢溫緊<br />\n但真係搵多我一秒都冇時間咩<br />\n琴日唔舒服 我驚有事<br />\n第一個就打比佢 點知佢唔聽<br />\n打左2/3次佢即cut<br />\nWhatsapp話佢上緊堂<br />\n打比其他朋友 仲快過佢聽<br />\n我個刻先明白 原來我係佢心目中<br />\n真係咩都唔係<br />\n我同佢whatsapp講話好緊要 你去一去廁所先啦<br />\n佢仲好唔耐煩咁話咩 我執埋野先搵你啦 <br />\n<br />\n好灰 我同佢拍左2年多少少 以為會長長久久<br />\n我唔想呢一刻同佢講分手 一講就影響佢溫習<br />\n我應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962a8aacf61bb30280f1cead3223a67b2d651a3a","tid":1936751,"uid":154093,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"可能上緊堂行唔開呢 你又唔whatsapp話佢知你咩事 咁就想分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f8bbd21cda06d895b6b2413dda0e4ae764e5e9","tid":1936751,"uid":231583,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:06:55.000Z","msg":"你唔舒服就睇醫生食藥啦打比條仔把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />洗唔洗急到要人上緊堂衝去廁所聽呀"},{"pid":"01ba08a88468cc029e336987118be3db8ffda397","tid":1936751,"uid":166245,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:08:45.000Z","msg":"你情感上想依賴佢"},{"pid":"e64fd76d48364fdf9b5207425cb3d63887cb7a21","tid":1936751,"uid":129506,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:09:53.000Z","msg":"你唔捨得講分手就等綠帽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條男擺明淡尻左 等緊散"},{"pid":"0bc842e5223cd45976b5fe9712dc47f39eab9a33","tid":1936751,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-21T12:10:43.000Z","msg":"兩年pink 西都反皮啦"},{"pid":"48bfccfaaaa96146c32cd2dd840eadb1f51e841c",